<!doctype html>
<html>

	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title>Hello MUI</title>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/mui.min.css">
	</head>
	<style type="text/css">

	</style>

	<body style="background:#f5f4f4;">
		<header id="header" class="mui-bar mui-bar-nav">
			<a class="mui-action-back mui-icon mui-icon-left-nav mui-pull-left" style="color:#000"></a>
			<h1 class="mui-title">体检返费</h1>
		</header>

		<div class="mui-scroll-wrapper" style="margin-top:55px;">
			<div class="mui-scroll cjs" style="background: #fff;padding-bottom: 100px;border-bottom:1px solid #ccc;margin-bottom: 50px;">
				<div style="width:100%;height:130px;border-bottom:1px solid #bdbdbd;padding:10px 30px;">
					<div style="background: url(../../images/scfp.png) center center no-repeat;background-size:90%,100%;width:19%;height:100%;float:left;margin-right:1%;position:relative;"><span style="color:#29b2f6;font-size:14px;position: absolute;bottom: 0px;">上传发票</span></div>
					<div style="background: url(../../images/tjjt.png) center center no-repeat;background-size:90%,100%;width:5%;height:100%;float:left;margin-right:1%;"></div>
					<div style="background: url(../../images/ljqd.png) center center no-repeat;background-size:90%,100%;width:19%;height:100%;float:left;margin-right:1%;position:relative;"><span style="color:#29b2f6;font-size:14px;position: absolute;bottom: 0px;">立即签到</span></div>
					<div style="background: url(../../images/tjjt.png) center center no-repeat;background-size:90%,100%;width:5%;height:100%;float:left;margin-right:1%;"></div>
					<div onclick="sczl()" style="background: url(../../images/sczl.png) center center no-repeat;background-size:90%,100%;width:19%;height:100%;float:left;margin-right:1%;position:relative;"><span style="color:#29b2f6;font-size:14px;position: absolute;bottom: 0px;">上传资料</span></div>
					<div style="background: url(../../images/tjjt.png) center center no-repeat;background-size:90%,100%;width:5%;height:100%;float:left;margin-right:1%;"></div>
					<div style="background: url(../../images/wftx.png) center center no-repeat;background-size:90%,100%;width:19%;height:100%;float:left;position:relative;"><span style="color:#29b2f6;font-size:14px;position: absolute;bottom: 0px;">无法提现</span></div>
				
				</div>
				<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:60px;margin-bottom:120px;">
					<p style="color:#000;font-size: 20px;font-weight: 500;">你本月已签到<span style="padding:0px 5px;color:#ff2432;font-size: 30px;">8</span>天</p>
					<p style="color:#000;font-size: 20px;font-weight: 500;">距离领取体检返费还差7天</p>
				</div>
				<div style="box-shadow: 0 0px 8px #ccc;width:90%;height:250px;margin:10px auto;position:relative;">
					<div style="width:38%;height:30px;background: #3cace3;position: absolute;top:20px;left:-13px;">
						<p style="color:#fff;line-height: 30px;padding:0 10px;font-size: 16px;">体检返费说明</p>
						<img src="../../images/tysj.png" alt="" style="position: absolute;top:30px;left:0px;" />
					</div>
					<div style="padding:60px 10px 10px;">
						<p style="color:#5d5d5d;">①只有用户通过直招帮申请入职后才可以申请报销体检费。</p>
						<p style="color:#5d5d5d;">②正式入职后，可上传效体检费用发票，审核通过后签到 有效。
						</p>
						<p style="color:#5d5d5d;">③签到满15天后，用户可以提交银行卡等提现资料，客服 将在3个工作日内完成审核。
						</p>
						<p style="color:#5d5d5d;">④最终解释权归直招帮所有。</p>
					</div>

				</div>

			</div>

		</div>

		<script src="../../js/mui.min.js"></script>
		<script>
			var deceleration = mui.os.ios ? 0.003 : 0.0009;
			mui('.mui-scroll-wrapper').scroll({
				bounce: true,
				indicators: true, //是否显示滚动条
				deceleration: deceleration,
				scrollX: true, //是否横向滚动
			});
			function sczl(){
				mui.openWindow({
					url: 'sczl.html',
					id: 'sczl.html'
				})
			}
		</script>
	</body>

</html>